    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >道场在等待着你……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上赛博武士之路，加入我们的 Discord 社区！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 《<strong>无明天道：江户之黯——序章</strong>》为游戏的免费试玩版。您可以体验游戏剧情、关卡与首领战，一窥“黯”的过去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新的、黑暗的、被机械占据的江户时代，幕府用以公正而无情的铁手统治者日本，而你就是幕府的执行人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你服从命令，遵循指示，杀死敌人……直到丧命为止。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >序章的故事发生在幽影城，一度光辉璀璨的日本大都会，而你在这里遭遇了滑铁卢。你被极为强大的对手击败，被丢在了废弃的摩天大楼之下的黑暗中。当你醒来之后，你将不得不以“另一种视角”来观察周围曾熟悉的一切……但你周围的世界，又有哪些是真实的呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你只能依靠损坏的传感器，与导师“天狗”的指引，领悟生存之道。在充满疯狂、幻想与科幻元素的古代神话世界之中变得越来越强大，踏上目不视物的愤怒之路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >——充满数据与谎言的世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鬼之面具模拟你周遭的环境，但务必当心：过期的数据只会让你看到过去充满欺骗的回声。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832220/extras/77b624d355292933a5c9e71ae6da2fd9.poster.avif?t=1729498022\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832220/extras/77b624d355292933a5c9e71ae6da2fd9.webm?t=1729498022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832220/extras/77b624d355292933a5c9e71ae6da2fd9.mp4?t=1729498022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >——无形之剑，最为致命</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即便目不能视，你也依然势不可挡。使用各种不同的传感器来探测敌人，找到敌人的弱点，然后以迅雷不及掩耳之势粉碎他们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832220/extras/ee2656aa545c709883fe6121c1a959f8.poster.avif?t=1729498022\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832220/extras/ee2656aa545c709883fe6121c1a959f8.webm?t=1729498022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832220/extras/ee2656aa545c709883fe6121c1a959f8.mp4?t=1729498022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >——赛博版日本民间故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现几十个赛博版日本民间故事，面对传说中的生物！找到它们的弱点，以毁灭性的终结技将它们逐个消灭！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832220/extras/4a642993e6ac7a1957b3d5ed3a039cbc.poster.avif?t=1729498022\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832220/extras/4a642993e6ac7a1957b3d5ed3a039cbc.webm?t=1729498022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832220/extras/4a642993e6ac7a1957b3d5ed3a039cbc.mp4?t=1729498022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >——遗失已久的机械传说</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的传感器已经刺破了历史的帷幕。通过声音、气味与热量来探索这个世界，揭开隐藏了几个世纪的传说，引导“黯”踏上复仇之路，体验精彩跌宕的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832220/extras/137db23d0322a148ede53b28fb6aa63f.poster.avif?t=1729498022\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832220/extras/137db23d0322a148ede53b28fb6aa63f.webm?t=1729498022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832220/extras/137db23d0322a148ede53b28fb6aa63f.mp4?t=1729498022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
